    <h2>ASTROPHOTOGRAPHY</h2>
    <p>You may be wondering how astounding it feels to
       represent the organising team of NSSC 16. If you want to share the same, National Students’
       Space Challenge presents you Student Ambassador Program. Selected Students will get a
       chance to work with the organising team of NSSC 2016 and a certificate certified by ISRO is
       also guaranteed. Goodies worth INR 5000 are promised along with free entry in NSSC’16</p>
